body:
The Jenkins failure for `Linux CPU Test Makefile` seems to be related to permissions on Jenkins server?
```
rm -rf /workspace/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/gen
rm: cannot remove '/workspace/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/gen/obj/tensorflow/core/graph/mkl_tfconversion_pass.o': Permission denied
rm: cannot remove '/workspace/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/gen/obj/tensorflow/core/graph/graph_partition.o': Permission denied
rm: cannot remove '/workspace/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/gen/obj/tensorflow/core/graph/mkl_layout_pass.o': Permission denied
```
